What's New in NVIDIA AI Enterprise.Hello, <br>
<br>
Here are product release highlights from the past few weeks in NVIDIA AI En=
terprise:
<br>
<ul>
<li>NVIDIA Riva Canary 1B ASR/AST and NVIDIA Riva Parakeet Taiwanese Mandar=
in Are Now Available as Downloadable NIM </li>
<li>3 NIM Optimized for NVIDIA DGX Spark Are Now Available</li>
</ul>
<br>
<b>NVIDIA Riva Canary 1B ASR/AST and NVIDIA Riva Parakeet Taiwanese Mandari=
n Are Now Available as Downloadable NIM</b>
<br> <br>




NVIDIA Riva Canary 1B ASR/AST is a multimodal model for speech to text reco=
gnition (ASR) in 26 languages and speech to text translation (AST) in 34 la=
nguages. Trained using NVIDIA=E2=80=99s Granary dataset using a FastConform=
er Encoder and a Transformer Decoder, the model supports .wav and .flac aud=
io files for input, and outputs text, including automatic punctuation and c=
apitalization. The new model is offline ready with In-Flight Batch Mode (IB=
D) and has improved accuracy and throughput. It replaces Canary 1B and Cana=
ry 0.6 Turbo, which are now deprecated.




<br><br>
NVIDIA Riva Parakeet 0.6B Taiwanese Mandarin is trained on an ASR dataset w=
ith around 90 hours of Taiwanese Mandarin (zh-TW) speech.&nbsp;
<br><br>
NVIDIA Riva Magpie TTS Multilingual NIM has added Mandarin, in addition to =
English, Spanish, French and German, and now supports up to 64 concurrent s=
treams via REST and WebSocket APIs.&nbsp;
<br><br>
All three NIM are available for commercial use with a NVIDIA AI Enterprise =
license.
<br><br><br>

Resources:
<br>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nim/teams/nvidia/contain=
ers/canary-1b?version=3D1.4.0" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>Get NVIDIA Riva Canary 1=
B ASR/AST NIM</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://build.nvidia.com/nvidia/parakeet-ctc-0_6b-zh-tw" rel=
=3D"nofollow"><u>Get NVIDIA Riva Parakeet for Taiwanese</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://build.nvidia.com/nvidia/magpie-tts-multilingual" rel=
=3D"nofollow"><u>Get NVIDIA Riva Magpie TTS Multilingual</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/nim/riva/asr/latest/overview.html" r=
el=3D"nofollow"><u>NVIDIA Riva ASR NIM Documentation</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://docs.nvidia.com/nim/riva/tts/latest/support-matrix.h=
tml#magpie-tts-multilingual" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>NVIDIA Riva Magpie TTS NIM=
 Support Matrix</u></a></li>








</ul>
<br><br>




<b>3 NIM Optimized for NVIDIA DGX Spark Are Now Available
</b>
<br><br>
NVIDIA Nemotron Nano 9B v2, Meta Llama 3.1 8B and Alibaba Qwen 3 32B are av=
ailable as downloadable NIM optimized for NVIDIA DGX Spark.&nbsp;
<br><br>
DGX Spark systems, built on the NVIDIA GB10 Grace Blackwell Superchip, deli=
ver up to 1 petaflop of AI performance in a compact desktop form factor, gi=
ving developers the power to run inference on AI models with up to 200B par=
ameters and fine-tune models of up to 70B parameters locally. The systems a=
lso feature 128GB of CPU-GPU coherent memory and NVIDIA NVLink-C2C technolo=
gy for high-speed connection.
<br><br>
The NVIDIA AI software stack is preinstalled on DGX Spark to enable develop=
ers to start working on AI projects out of the box.&nbsp;

<br><br><br>
Resources:
<br>
<ul>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nim/teams/nvidia/contain=
ers/nvidia-nemotron-nano-9b-v2-dgx-spark?version=3D1.0.0-variant" rel=3D"no=
follow"><u>Get NVIDIA Nemotron Nano 9B NIM for DGX Spark</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nim/teams/meta/container=
s/llama-3.1-8b-instruct-dgx-spark?version=3D1.0.0-variant" rel=3D"nofollow"=
>
<u>Get Meta Llama 3.1 8B NIM for DGX Spark</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://catalog.ngc.nvidia.com/orgs/nim/teams/qwen/container=
s/qwen3-32b-dgx-spark?version=3D1.0" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>Get Alibaba Qwen 3=
 32B NIM for DGX Spark</u></a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://nvidianews.nvidia.com/news/nvidia-dgx-spark-arrives-=
for-worlds-ai-developers" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>NVIDIA DGX Spark Arrives for =
World=E2=80=99s AI Developers</u></a></li>
</ul>
