<br>
<b>NVIDIA Riva Canary 1B ASR/AST and NVIDIA Riva Parakeet Taiwanese Mandari=
n Are Now Available as Downloadable NIM</b>
<br> <br>




NVIDIA Riva Canary 1B ASR/AST is a multimodal model for speech to text reco=
gnition (ASR) in 26 languages and speech to text translation (AST) in 34 la=
nguages. Trained using NVIDIA=E2=80=99s Granary dataset using a FastConform=
er Encoder and a Transformer Decoder, the model supports .wav and .flac aud=
io files for input, and outputs text, including automatic punctuation and c=
apitalization. The new model is offline ready with In-Flight Batch Mode (IB=
D) and has improved accuracy and throughput. It replaces Canary 1B and Cana=
ry 0.6 Turbo, which are now deprecated.




<br><br>
NVIDIA Riva Parakeet 0.6B Taiwanese Mandarin is trained on an ASR dataset w=
ith around 90 hours of Taiwanese Mandarin (zh-TW) speech.&nbsp;
<br><br>
NVIDIA Riva Magpie TTS Multilingual NIM has added Mandarin, in addition to =
English, Spanish, French and German, and now supports up to 64 concurrent s=
treams via REST and WebSocket APIs.&nbsp;
<br><br>
All three NIM are available for commercial use with a NVIDIA AI Enterprise =
license.
<br><br><br>

