ailable as downloadable NIM optimized for NVIDIA DGX Spark.&nbsp;
<br><br>
DGX Spark systems, built on the NVIDIA GB10 Grace Blackwell Superchip, deli=
ver up to 1 petaflop of AI performance in a compact desktop form factor, gi=
ving developers the power to run inference on AI models with up to 200B par=
ameters and fine-tune models of up to 70B parameters locally. The systems a=
lso feature 128GB of CPU-GPU coherent memory and NVIDIA NVLink-C2C technolo=
gy for high-speed connection.
<br><br>
